# MOBILE-FIRST

## BREAKPOINTS
768px (tablet/mobile) | 1024px (desktop) | 1280px (large)

## CSS
Mobile base: .nav { display: none; } | Desktop: @media (min-width: 768px) { .nav { display: flex; } }

## TOUCH TARGETS (WCAG 2.1 AAA)
44x44px min, 48x48px recommended, spacing ≥8px

## VIEWPORT
width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=5.0, user-scalable=yes

## VAADIN
AppLayout: auto-overlay <768px (addToDrawer mobile, addToNavbar desktop) | FormLayout: ResponsiveStep("0", 1), ResponsiveStep("768px", 2) | Button: @media (max-width: 767px) hide label ::part(label), 44x44px, center icon

## ANTIPATTERNS
Fixed widths → max-width: 100% | user-scalable=no → accessibility violation | Touch <44px → WCAG fail | Desktop-first @media (max-width) → min-width | Font-size <16px → iOS zooms
